name: Wedding - Personalised Handmade Clutch Bag Commissions - Bridal
description:
Commissions 

Do you have leftover fabric from your wedding dress?

Don't just throw it away! Use the excess fabric and turn it into a bespoke clutch bag. 

 Details about clutch:

- fully lined
- Silver or antique brass frame
- UK handmade
 
Made to order - Please allow 4-5 weeks for production following payment

Dimensions - 10 inches x 4 inches (26cm x 10cm), 8 inch frame

I can also email photos of sequin fabric and other fabrics that I normally use to create my clutch bags.

Bridesmaids gifts

Custom clutch bags to match the bridesmaids dresses, send me your fabric and I will create the matching clutch bag for your bridesmaids. I include the bridesmaids names and wedding  your wedding details sewn into the lining of the bags. A gift they will treasure always!

Also, clutch bags made for Mother of the Bride or Groom's either framed bags or clasp fastening 

How do I order? 

Send me an email requesting a commission piece and I will get back to you with a quote or questions if I need more information.
Once we are happy I will create a listing for you to make payment.
I will begin to make your clutch bag following payment.
Use contact form located on footer to send inquiry
Please note: the price shown is not valid, this page is for examples only
